The paper also discusses the ambiguity introduced by quantized distances, which is a security concern and falls under the category of "Cryptography and Security" (cs.CR). The paper also mentions empirical data and state-of-the-art systems, which suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG and cs.CR, followed by cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.MM.
